Personally i had a great experience. Got some good tapas and received good service. My wife really liked the food we ordered and was super happy so naturally, I was super happy. The night we went there its was ran by a bunch of 20 something year old Spanish hipster dudes, all of them we're super nice and selected some good music through out the evening. Not a fancy joint but more like a cool vibey restaurant that serves up some kick ass tapas.
